title: Re-Live Your Life
itunes:title: Re-Live Your Life
description:
Episode 300 - What if you could go back an re-live certain parts of your life as the person you are now? How much different would your life be if you could see certain experiences as a mature adult instead of child? What difference would that make in your life? We're going to chat about that in this episode.
